# ───── Internal / operator-only notes ─────
# Keep BRD, STATUS, PROGRESS, HANDOFF, TODO, NOTES etc. out of the public repo.
# Anchored at repo root so nested `src/internal/**` source modules stay tracked.
/internal/
# Bundle analyzer artifacts — emitted by `pnpm analyze` into /internal/, but
# listed explicitly so contributors can grep this file and know what they are.
/internal/bundle-stats.jsonl
/internal/bundle-visualizer-treemap.html
/internal/bundle-visualizer-sunburst.html
/internal/bundle-visualizer-network.html
vis/
.meta-v2-review/

# ───── AI / assistant tooling artifacts ─────
.claude/
.aider*
.cursor/
.continue/
.agents/
.opencode/

# Project-local Claude memory + project-instructions files. Operator-only;
# track via internal/ if a public mirror is needed.
/CLAUDE.md
/MEMORY.md
/AGENTS.md
.mcp.json

# ───── Nightly cron workflow ─────
# Per-firing logs and the lock file — generated, do not commit.
.nightrun/*.jsonl
.nightrun/.lock
.nightrun/
/PROGRESS.md

# ───── Misc ─────
*.local
